### 5. Using `dplyr` Choice Functions (20 points)

```{r}
library(dplyr)
library(lterdatasampler)
```

5a
```{r}
crab_size <- 17

if_else(crab_size >= 20, "large", "small")
```

5b
```{r}
if_else(crab_size > 20, "large",
        if_else(crab_size > 10, "medium", "small"))
```

