```{r}
get_mass_from_length_by_name(10, "Stegosauria")
```

4b
```{r}
get_mass_from_length_by_name(8, "Theropoda")
```

4c
```{r}
get_mass_from_length_by_name(12, "Sauropoda")
```

4d
```{r}
get_mass_from_length_by_name(13, 'Ankylosauria')
```

